
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Shopping Center Security Services | ShieldWise Security</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #1a3c6e;
            --secondary-color: #bf9e5b;
            --text-color: #333333;
            --light-bg: #f8f9fa;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(26, 60, 110, 0.9), rgba(26, 60, 110, 0.9)), url('/img/shoppingsecurity.webp');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            padding: 150px 0;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .service-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .feature-list li {
            padding: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 30px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .feature-list li:before {
            content: 'âœ“';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .cta-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), #0d2b54);
            padding: 80px 0;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .btn-custom {
            background: var(--secondary-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-custom:hover {
            background: #a88b4a;
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .stat-card {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .testimonial {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../Partials/Header') %>

    <main>
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="hero-title">Shopping Center Security Services</h1>
                <p class="lead">Professional security solutions for retail centers and shopping malls</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <section class="py-5">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                        <div class="service-card">
                            <h2 class="mb-4">Comprehensive Shopping Center Security Solutions</h2>
                            <p>At ShieldWise Security, we understand the unique security challenges faced by shopping centers and retail establishments. Our specialized security services ensure the safety of shoppers, staff, and property while maintaining a welcoming atmosphere for your customers.</p>
                            
                            <h3 class="mt-4">Our Shopping Center Security Services Include:</h3>
                            <ul class="feature-list">
                                <li>Retail Loss Prevention</li>
                                <li>Parking Lot Security Patrols</li>
                                <li>Access Control Management</li>
                                <li>CCTV Monitoring</li>
                                <li>Emergency Response Protocol</li>
                                <li>Crowd Management</li>
                                <li>After-Hours Security</li>
                                <li>Special Event Security Coverage</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Statistics -->
                <div class="row mt-5">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="stat-card">
                            <div class="stat-number">200+</div>
                            <div>Shopping Centers Protected</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="stat-card">
                            <div class="stat-number">24/7</div>
                            <div>Security Coverage</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="stat-card">
                            <div class="stat-number">15+</div>
                            <div>Years Experience</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Testimonials -->
                <div class="row mt-5">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="testimonial">
                            <p class="mb-3">"ShieldWise's security team has significantly improved the safety at our shopping center. Their professional approach and customer service are outstanding."</p>
                            <strong>- Robert Chen</strong><br>
                            <small>Mall Operations Director, Pacific Shopping Center</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="testimonial">
                            <p class="mb-3">"Since partnering with ShieldWise, we've seen a dramatic reduction in security incidents. Their team's responsiveness is exceptional."</p>
                            <strong>- Sarah Thompson</strong><br>
                            <small>Property Manager, Retail Solutions Inc.</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <section class="cta-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="mb-4">Secure Your Shopping Center Today</h2>
                <p class="mb-4">Contact us for a customized shopping center security solution</p>
                <a href="/get-quote" class="btn btn-custom">Get a Free Quote</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('../Partials/Footer') %>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
